        <abstract> 
<p>Is sending CD his <hi rend="italic">Illustrated book of poultry</hi> in which the chapter on the "Origin of the domestic fowl" may be of interest.</p>  
<p>He ventures to mention several errors in <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Mentions the late Mr Lane of Bristol, a celebrated Spanish breeder (of poultry).</p>
        </abstract>
